articles.title: Footballer Danelle Tan Is 1st Female S'porean To Play In Europe, Helps Score Goal On Debut - MS News
articles.description: Footballer Danelle Tan has become the first female Singaporeans to play in a European league. A pass she made on her debut led to a goal.
articles.content:
